casebody.data:
Fred S. Schlesinger, Respondent-Appellant, v. Charles Punia et al., Individually and as Copartners Doing Business under the Name of Punia & Marx, Defendants, and Cleveland Realty Corp., Appellant-Respondent.

Order unanimously affirmed, without costs. No opinion. The date for the examination to proceed to he fixed in the order. Settle order on notice. Present— Martin, P. J., Townley, Glennon, Cohn and Callahan, JJ.
